    }
  ]
}
```

## Rules

- ALL names MUST be distinct from the tracked/dismissed lists above (case-insensitive)
- ALL `careers_url` entries MUST be real URLs you verified via web search
- ALL `why_relevant` entries MUST reference something current or resume-specific — NOT generic ("great company", "innovative culture")
- Keep the `source` field as exactly `"adjacent"` or `"discovery"`
- 8 minimum, 10 maximum; each list at least 3
- Output ONLY the JSON object
